{"tid":2301560,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"生活苦澀","createTime":"2020-11-26T11:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T11:58:08.000Z","uid":350275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c71d85922a9a50c1fbd1e3726313212462f0b5","tid":2301560,"uid":350275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:46:49.000Z","msg":"呢排工作量越嚟越多，開始覺得好大壓力<br />\n早幾日屋企人又岀咗事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時同女朋友感情唔多好，完全傾唔到心事，但又要聽佢呻，又要遷就佢。<br />\n我而家覺得自己就嚟爆煲，淨係不斷輸入，冇得輸出，好頭痛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岀街又要戴個口罩，以前都可以就咁落街散心，而家落個街呼吸都要錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0f713466bf2d269d7c1092c02db29078dc20c8","tid":2301560,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:57:52.000Z","msg":"執咪有 使乜錢"},{"pid":"5701be15c9aaa3bad91e1d2ba046b6345b78b0bc","tid":2301560,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:58:08.000Z","msg":"同條女分撚左手佢，踢鳩佢走，之後唔撈，返屋企訓教！"}]}